info.author: Norman Lorrain
info.description:
This collection of Python scripts creates an AutoRun executable for Windows. The
autorun contains an HTTP server with embedded search engine, powered by the
excellent swish-e project.
info.name: AutoSwish
info.summary: CD autoplay HTTP server with embedded search engine
